n=m
\sum_{1\le r\le m}(2r-1)=m^2
P(m+1): \sum_{1\le r\le m+1}(2r-1)=\sum_{1\le r\le m}(2r-1)+2m+1=m^2+2m+1=(m+1)^2
P(m+1)
