b):
(r+1)^3-r^3=3r^2+3r+1
r=1,2,\cdots,n-1,n
(n+1)^3-1=3\sum_{1\le r\le n}r^2+3\sum_{1\le r\le n}r+\sum_{1\le r\le n}1
\sum_{1\le r\le n}r=\frac{n(n+1)}2
\sum_{1\le r\le n}1=n
\sum_{1\le r\le n}r^2=\frac{n(n+1)(2n+1)}6
